text.section:
The county clerk shall collect any applicable sales and use tax for the following tangible personal property purchased out of state at the time the property is offered for titling or first registration:
Recreational vehicles as defined in KRS 186.650;
Manufactured homes as defined in KRS 186.650;
Motorboats as defined in KRS 235.010;
Vessels as defined in KRS 235.010; and
Any other tangible personal property offered for titling or first registration in Kentucky.
